service.name: (CDAM)  Repository API
service.description:
Repository API for Code DAM project that allows clients to handle their assets:

store and retrieve assets
store and retrieve some key, low-level metadata for the assets
archive or remove assets
https://cdamrepositoryapi.docs.apiary.io
